  "detailed_description": "Hello, Cadet!<br>Welcome to Cosmic Pew Pew, an intergalactic shipping company. Are you ready to begin your training for piloting the clumsiest spaceship in the galaxy?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166110/extras/88586e3efafb2b64daea4e97807e882c.poster.avif?t=1736455463\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166110/extras/88586e3efafb2b64daea4e97807e882c.webm?t=1736455463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166110/extras/88586e3efafb2b64daea4e97807e882c.mp4?t=1736455463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You'll face simulations that challenge your piloting skills in various scenarios. It won't be easy! Sometimes you'll need to pick up cargo, and other times you'll have to drop it off. After all, you're training with an intergalactic shipping company!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166110/extras/7c97281bed2567f15993e7e06f9bd8fa.poster.avif?t=1736455463\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166110/extras/7c97281bed2567f15993e7e06f9bd8fa.webm?t=1736455463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166110/extras/7c97281bed2567f15993e7e06f9bd8fa.mp4?t=1736455463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Sometimes, you’ll have to forge your own path by blasting through obstacles to clear the way! Your spaceship comes fully equipped with a variety of features, allowing for thrilling and unpredictable gameplay. Get ready for some wild, out-of-this-world adventures!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166110/extras/123fe44754985331d4190ff9719f653d.poster.avif?t=1736455463\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166110/extras/123fe44754985331d4190ff9719f653d.webm?t=1736455463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166110/extras/123fe44754985331d4190ff9719f653d.mp4?t=1736455463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
